caption.title: Chemical composition of Pinus sylvestris and Wollemia nobilis resin.
caption.p: Compounds in bold are only present in one of the two resins. The compounds are ordered based on the difference in % area between the two resins; the first rows are more concentrated in P. sylvestris resin, and the bottom rows are more concentrated in W. nobilis resin.
